==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Chromatype
<hw>Chro"ma*type</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ color +
<?/ type.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Photog.)</fld> <def>A colored photographic picture
taken upon paper made sensitive with potassium bichromate or some other
salt of chromium.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The process by which such picture is made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Chrome</ent>⟦br⟧
